data.description: ***Price Improved***Step into the home of your dreams! This immaculately renovated two-level home seamlessly combines modern sophistication with enduring comfort. As you enter, you'll step into a realm of convenience and style, where thoughtful design takes center stage.  The open-concept living area, drenched in natural light, sets the stage for daily life and social gatherings. From the gleaming wood floors to the fresh paint and elegant granite countertops, every detail has been considered to make this home a perfect 10.  An exceptional opportunity awaits to claim this renovated home as your personal sanctuary. Ready to entertain? Head downstairs to the above-ground, fully finished basement, complete with a separate entrance and a full bathroom, creating a versatile space for your guests.  Embrace the seasons as you enjoy endless summer days or cozy autumn evenings on the deck or by the firepit. This home, with its remarkable blend of style and function, is a rare find, so act swiftly as it won't stay on the market for long!
